Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:55.22,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:56.93,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?!  Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.75,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you burn them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:15:59.79,Chiha-internaloverlap,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,There goes 10% of her concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:03.52,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!  Why would you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:03.03,Chiha-internaloverlap,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,So this is why Sudo acts like a sadist...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.23,blackt,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}I see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:06.64,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Arata...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:10.64,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,In your world, there's no \Nsuch thing as a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:13.46,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Call me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.62,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I really hope
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:20.42,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to burn your Daddy Bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:23.38,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:26.04,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,The president is turning into a sadist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:44.01,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Naniwa Bay, now the flower \Nblooms, but for winter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:52.49,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Here comes spring, now the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:52.49,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,When reading cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:54.72,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,the second verse should \Ntake four seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:17:01.90,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Here comes spring, now the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:56.89,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,with three seconds of fade out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:59.06,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Then you pause for one second,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:01.29,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,before reading the first verse of \Nthe next poem in five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:03.58,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:09.78,Chiha-poem,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Note that though we may \Nbe apart, if I am to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:05.58,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I was late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:09.19,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:12.32,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,The players spend that second focused
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:14.18,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,on the next sound to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.99,Chiha-poem,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}May the time we spend apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:18.14,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my voice jumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.69,Chiha-poem,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The hazy field of reeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:21.52,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:23.65,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:30.14,Chiha-poem,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}but I cannot hide the love I \Nfeel for one who is so dear
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:27.24,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,The reader must stay completely \Nfocused for an entire hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:29.52,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's not an easy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:31.00,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:37.87,Chiha-poem,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Since I could not hide my love,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:35.38,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,while it may be difficult now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:37.87,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,the president will make Class A one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:44.69,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody wants to give up their dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:50.63,chalkboard,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Club Advisor Meeting\NBudget\NRoom Space\NScheduling
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:47.77,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:50.63,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to assign the Karuta \NClub's room to the Concert Band?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:52.88,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:57.14,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,However, the room is too \Nbig for an arts club
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:59.08,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that only has five members.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:01.40,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Concert Band has forty members,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:02.85,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so they need the space.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:05.62,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Karuta Club could simply \Nuse an empty classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:07.69,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I beg to differ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:12.02,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta requires a \Nsoundproof environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:15.03,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,The location can't have students
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:17.91,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,walking through the hallways \Nor athletes practicing nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:19.46,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,However, Ms. Miyauchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:20.88,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,The Karuta Club advanced
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:24.39,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to the national championship\N in their first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:27.68,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,The members also placed first and \Nsecond in sanctioned tournaments!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:31.17,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there will be many \Nnew members this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.58,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,You will see excellent results!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.89,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Could you at least
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:39.55,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,let the Concert Band use the second floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:44.26,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I just said that karuta requires \Na soundproof environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:45.06,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.04,dude,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:49.56,miya,All,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1)}Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.93,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,The empress...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:55.69,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Miyauchi cares about \Nthe Karuta Club very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.69,tissue,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(125,1)}Tissues?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:01.80,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fukasaku, the classical \Nliterature teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:05.20,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,The professor's the only person \Nthe empress can't overwhelm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:07.52,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,How does this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:11.14,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,If there are five new members next year,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:13.21,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll leave everything as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:18.35,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta is a wonderful art.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:21.72,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that it will be easy \Nto recruit five members.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:23.67,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:26.60,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't recruit five members, \Nwe will return the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:32.00,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I wanted to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:33.69,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Five members...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:39.14,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Recruit five members to that \Nincredibly niche club?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:43.49,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:45.49,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:47.65,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,From the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:09.31,handwriting,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Notice:\N\NIf the Karuta Club does not recruit \Nfive new members next year,\Nyou will have to return the clubroom.\NGood luck. ( {\b1};{\b0} △ {\b1};{\b0} )\N\N I was able to increase the \Nclub's budget to 30,000 yen.\N\NMiyauchi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.86,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Five people?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:11.67,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:14.44,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,A-An emoticon?  And it's handwritten...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:18.57,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty thousand yen budget!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:20.45,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you care about, Kana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:26.95,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:27.85,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The younger sister of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:29.85,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the model Ayase Chitose \Nis a second-year here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:31.28,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,No way!  I'm a fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:32.37,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go check her out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:37.84,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:46.87,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:46.47,club,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Please come see Ayase Chihaya in class 2-9!!\NLet's start a competitive karuta club!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:49.15,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:50.71,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Track pants?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:52.23,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,And look at the belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:54.03,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:56.82,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,You're an upperclassman now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.82,0:20:59.69,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,yet you're still embarrassing yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:03.13,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Right, everyone was saying \Nhow she's pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:03.13,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  You ended up \Nfailing your final exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:06.09,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}but it's wasted as soon as \Nshe talks or does something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:06.87,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,After you were able to ever so slightly \Nimprove your grades last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:08.37,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Beauty in vain...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:26.54,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,And Ayase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.51,0:22:30.15,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Put another one up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.13,0:22:34.65,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's play karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.65,0:22:36.65,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,
